{"tid":521933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【終極FF】陳文敏冀律政司司長一地兩檢本地立法階段維護司法制度","createTime":"2018-01-07T05:27:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T06:16:55.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2d44753640eebfaf9a3df2044e9066f8b51249cb","tid":521933,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1373790_1_20180107123608.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1373790_1_20180107123608.jpg&h=d6afa3bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有份參加大律師公會改選的港大法律學院教授陳文敏說，擔心在一地兩檢議題上，如果有人提出司法覆核，人大會再次釋法，衝擊本港的司法制度；他希望特區政府反思現有安排是否唯一可行方案。<br />\n<br />\n陳文敏又期望，新任律政司司長在本地立法階段「閘得住無法理依據的安排」， 維護本港司法制度。"},{"pid":"62cdbaf5599737f2923406a920e555a4f2dc1071","tid":521933,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:32:09.000Z","msg":"陳文敏要求一隻獅子唔食肉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a79226cb00eb452767bd6befe7d6626dde8e23d","tid":521933,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T06:15:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a8daee76fd8a2d30668f697d0aaf9fd744950d9","tid":521933,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T06:16:55.000Z","msg":"好過唔講"}]}